      • createTVSearchEmbed

        public net.dv8tion.jda.api.EmbedBuilder createTVSearchEmbed​(TvSearch[] resultArray,
                                                            int resultNum)
        Creates a TvSearch Embed
        Takes in a TvSearch array and the desired index number to form a EmbedBuilder object containing a show's:
        • Name
        • Description
        • TVDb ID
        • Original Airing Network
        • Airing status {Running | Ended}
        • Cover art
        • Page Number (place in array + 1)
        Parameters:
        resultArray - A TvSearch array with all values filled
        resultNum - The index of the show that needs to be put into an embed.
        Returns:
        A EmbedBuilder object containing above information.
